front.title: Single Trooper Aerial Platform
front.gametext: May add 1 pilot. May move as a 'react'. When piloted by a battle droid, vehicle and pilot are immune to attrition < 4. Pilot's power = 0. If lost, character aboard may 'jump off' (disembark).
front.lore: STAPs are used by infantry battle droids to provide a variety of range-based advantages on the battlefield.
